<p>
	Nothing old, this week! Yep, that&#39;s right &mdash; this week&#39;s Mac Geek Gab podcast finds Dave, John, and Pilot Pete going through topics and issues they&#39;ve never discussed in the previous 422 episodes. They talk about using clamshell mode, how to use OnyX properly, running Fusion Drive on older Macs, issues with USB-powered drives and Time Capsules, Skype vs. Little Snitch, and MUCH more. Download today &mdash; it&#39;s free and you&#39;ll love it. We promise!</p>
